data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
In music, the term note has two primary meanings: 1. A sign used in to represent the relative duration and pitch of a sound 2. A pitched sound itself.
Notes are the "atoms" of much Western music
Absolute notes:
C - D - E - F - G - A - B refer to the absolute notes
Absolute notes and sharp notes:
C D E F G A C #-D# F#G# A#
